descriptionHTML:
Pimp your watch with Summer Sand Watch Face. Clean and fast interfase for summer holidays use.

Install App -> Go to Android Wear -> Choose Summer Sand Watch Face

The sunny beach watch face hase been testig on Moto 360, LG G Watch R, ASUS ZenWatch, Sony SmartWatch and other.
